{"tid":1099600,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新居屋第二滴血　凱樂苑一高層單位買家撻訂","createTime":"2019-04-10T01:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T08:27:35.000Z","uid":73092,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"dce9776e797bc164e72b7cbc0d7266e713a48523","tid":1099600,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:18:01.000Z","msg":"今期居屋再出現撻訂，成為開售後「第二滴血」。繼啟德啟朗苑出現早前首宗撻訂後，長沙灣凱樂苑A座39樓09室今日(9日)撤銷買賣協議，該單位在3月13日簽訂買賣協議，成交價為3,502,600港元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前啟德啟朗苑B座25樓10室撤銷買賣協議，該單位早在3月1日簽訂買賣協議，成交金額2,183,400港元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今期居屋反應熱烈，房屋委員會收到27.2萬份申請，超額認購60.3倍，申請創下新高。而今期居屋出售合共4431個單位，以市價52折定價，包括長沙灣凱樂苑、啟德啟朗苑及東涌裕泰苑，售價介乎118萬至468萬港元，2月28日開始揀樓。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"444948abf4494a168515745e459e985cbbe00885","tid":1099600,"uid":164387,"like":39,"dislike":9,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f21ce561deb29deca33166d349a8e93e4aa35e0","tid":1099600,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abe1411e2b261b36a407af651475d45abddf8bbc","tid":1099600,"uid":113277,"like":95,"dislike":5,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"三百萬仲可以按9成，30萬都拎唔出學人買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bb4d6e81be77a25c40062a7292c92f733292de","tid":1099600,"uid":38693,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"quote":{"pid":"abe1411e2b261b36a407af651475d45abddf8bbc","tid":1099600,"uid":113277,"like":95,"dislike":5,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"三百萬仲可以按9成，30萬都拎唔出學人買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"簽左買賣合同即係俾左首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢應該係過唔到tu"},{"pid":"c602118864318472f4645ae43068a732e21fe609","tid":1099600,"uid":179866,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"abe1411e2b261b36a407af6514